ue\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lym1665702585074.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lym1665702585074.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lym1665702585074.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lym1665702585074\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Field </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This\n      could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a\n      derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is\n      stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lym1665702585074__section_w4069ab1b5b1_w4070ab1b5_w4071ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lym1665702585074__section_w4072ab1b5b3_w4073ab1b5_w4074ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1018281e56\"> Characteristics </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"lym1665702585074__image_bxv_jmq_lwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/field.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">fld</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uqv1665702561461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uqv1665702561461.html\" title=\"An Entity is an abstract data type that defines a logical data aggregation and its associated default characteristics and behavior. It may be mapped to a table in a DBMS, and is most frequently used to represent the application data, but it can also represent transient data, a collection of controls, or constant data.\">Entity</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ulo1665702550460.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ulo1665702550460.html\" title=\"A Uniface Development Object is an abstract data type that defines the characteristics and behavior of a logical application unit, such as a Component, Field, Message, Library, and so on.\">Development Object</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zhd1665702557352.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zhd1665702557352.html\" title=\"A Modeled Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Modeled Entity.\">Modeled Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zyj1665702550619.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zyj1665702550619.html\" title=\"A Component Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in a Component Entity.\">Component Field</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aam1665702585156.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aam1665702585156.html\" title=\"A Derived Component Field references a Modeled Field and initially inherits its properties and code containers.\">Derived Component Field</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yvz1665702585231.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yvz1665702585231.html\" title=\"A database field is a Modeled Field whose Is External property is True, so it is also known as an external field. It can be used in database I/O.\">Database Field</a>,\n                              <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dtx1665702585306.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dtx1665702585306.html\" title=\"A non-database field is a Modeled Field or Component Field whose Is External property is F. It can be used for a control, constant data, derived data, or other non-persistent data. It cannot be used for database I/O or passing in an entity or occurrence parameter.\">Non-Database Field</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"lym1665702585074__table_d10505e1_d10506e1_d10507e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">fld:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FieldName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lym1665702585074__section_w4075ab1b5b5_w4076ab1b5_w4077ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1018281e319\"> Specialization </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94919e1_d94920e1_d94921e1\">Field is an abstract data type that specializes\n            Development Object in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37208e1_d37209e1_d37210e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94922e1_d94923e1_d94924e1\">It has an Entity as parent.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37211e1_d37212e1_d37213e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94925e1_d94926e1_d94927e1\">It has no child development objects.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lym1665702585074__section_w4078ab1b5b7_w4079ab1b5_w4080ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1018281e343\"> Properties </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94931e1_d94932e1_d94933e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37214e1_d37215e1_d37216e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37217e1_d37218e1_d37219e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37220e1_d37221e1_d37222e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37223e1_d37224e1_d37225e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37226e1_d37227e1_d37228e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94934e1_d94935e1_d94936e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37229e1_d37230e1_d37231e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jtg1665702585772.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jtg1665702585772.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the current object inherits from a modeled object. Boolean read-only.\">Inherits</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37232e1_d37233e1_d37234e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tgz1665702585851.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tgz1665702585851.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the development object from which the current object inherits. Depending on the context, it may be read-only or editable.\">Inherits From</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37235e1_d37236e1_d37237e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"puj1665702585966.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/puj1665702585966.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the entity or field is generic. Applicable only in modeled components.\">Is Generic</a> (only in modeled components)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37238e1_d37239e1_d37240e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sdh1665702586086.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sdh1665702586086.html\" title=\"This property indicates whether the entity or field is bound to a generic entity or field in a modeled component. Boolean read-only.\">Is Bound</a> (only in derived components)</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37241e1_d37242e1_d37243e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ljd1665702586171.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ljd1665702586171.html\" title=\"This property defines the name of the generic entity or field in a modeled component to which the current object is bound.\">Bound To</a> (only in derived components)</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94937e1_d94938e1_d94939e1\">Data I/O Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37244e1_d37245e1_d37246e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aww1665702586248.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aww1665702586248.html\" title=\"Uniface data type to use for this field, variable, or parameter. The default value is S (String).\">Data Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37247e1_d37248e1_d37249e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pta1665702586322.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pta1665702586322.html\" title=\"Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.\">Is External</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37250e1_d37251e1_d37252e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iri1665702586413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iri1665702586413.html\" title=\"Determines whether the field contents are same for all occurrences of the entity.\">Is Static</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37253e1_d37254e1_d37255e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oji1665702586488.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oji1665702586488.html\" title=\"Determines whether the field is a control field in a form component, meaning that it can be selected with the mouse but not get focus. This affects validation behavior.\">Is Control</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37256e1_d37257e1_d37258e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"enu1665702584272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/enu1665702584272.html\" title=\"This property (also known as the entity interface) determines how the data is mapped to the database.\">Database Interface (Entities)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37259e1_d37260e1_d37261e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zlt1665702557043.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zlt1665702557043.html\" title=\"The Field Syntax property specifies the input format for data, including the entry format (for example, 1-Dec-14 or 20141201), the allowed characters, and whether the field is mandatory or read-only.\">Field Syntax</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37262e1_d37263e1_d37264e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lpv1665702557117.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lpv1665702557117.html\" title=\"Property that specifies how the field's data is formatted for display. The value can be a comma-separated list of shorthand codes, or a reference to a modeled field layout.\">Field Layout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37265e1_d37266e1_d37267e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wen1665702586573.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wen1665702586573.html\" title=\"Value that should be displayed in this field at runtime; can be a default for the user or the actual field value.\">Initial Value</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lym1665702585074__p_d94940e1_d94941e1_d94942e1\">Presentation Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37268e1_d37269e1_d37270e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wcj1665702586648.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wcj1665702586648.html\" title=\"Type of widget to use for this entity or field in Form (and Report) components.\">FRM Widget Type (Field)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37271e1_d37272e1_d37273e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jry1665703064511.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jry1665703064511.html\">FRM Widget Properties for Entity</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kyz1665703064946.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kyz1665703064946.html\">FRM Widget Properties for Fields</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37274e1_d37275e1_d37276e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hlx1665702586727.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hlx1665702586727.html\" title=\"Type of logical widget to use for this entity or field in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.\">DSP Widget Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37277e1_d37278e1_d37279e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bed1665703061378.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bed1665703061378.html\">DSP Widget Properties</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37280e1_d37281e1_d37282e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nrq1665703106382.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nrq1665703106382.html\" title=\"Type of widget to use for this field in Static Server Page (USP) components.\">USP Widget Type</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ixd1665703106601.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ixd1665703106601.html\">USP Widget Properties</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37286e1_d37287e1_d37288e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nnt1665702586853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nnt1665702586853.html\" title=\"Name of the pop-up menu object to display when the user clicks the mouse button in this component, entity, or field.\">Pop-up Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37289e1_d37290e1_d37291e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xcr1665702586927.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xcr1665702586927.html\" title=\"Text of the label. If the label is attached to a field, it can be set in ProcScript using the $labelproperties function.\">Label Text</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37292e1_d37293e1_d37294e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37295e1_d37296e1_d37297e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37298e1_d37299e1_d37300e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37301e1_d37302e1_d37303e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37304e1_d37305e1_d37306e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gmd1665702587249.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gmd1665702587249.html\" title=\"This property determines whether a border is displayed around the area frame, entity or occurrence frame, or field. It is set from the context menu in the form canvas.\">Border</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"lym1665702585074__li_d37307e1_d37308e1_d37309e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pwl1704360251149.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Fields</a><p>A field is a unit of data in an entity. It usually represents a column in a database table, but it can model data that is not stored, such as a control or a derived field.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614492\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3614492\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Field Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Field A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: fld Main Development Object? No Part of: Entity Contains: Value, Property , Code Container Generalization: Development Object Specializations: Modeled Field , Component Field , Derived Component Field , Database Field , Non-Database Field Compilation Output — URI format: fld: FieldName Specialization Field is an abstract data type that specializes Development Object in the following ways: It has an Entity as parent. It has no child development objects. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Configuration Properties: Inherits Inherits From Is Generic (only in modeled components) Is Bound (only in derived components) Bound To (only in derived components) Data I/O Properties: Data Type Is External Is Static Is Control Database Interface (Entities) Field Syntax Field Layout Initial Value Presentation Properties: FRM Widget Type (Field) FRM Widget Properties for Entity FRM Widget Properties for Fields DSP Widget Type DSP Widget Properties USP Widget Type USP Widget Properties Pop-up Menu Label Text Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Border Index Color Related Links Fields A field is a unit of data in an entity. It usually represents a column in a database table, but it can model data that is not stored, such as a control or a derived field. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}